value.0: The Kaz'horks are hulking fiends who exchanged most brains for brawns. Unsurprisingly they make great shock troops.
The Knights of the Bastion are perfection incarnated and for that reason they hate change above all.
This armor is the mark of an elite member of the Cordorian Guard.
The great Halen, archmage of Mystra's Grove has recently commissioned these Anti-Magic (Summon) Wands for the Cordorian Guard!

The Cordorian Guards have developed an ingenious quill and parchment set with a compact carrying case for "on the job" and "on the spot" fining.
